      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p data-es="limbo/ existe porque la música independiente no podía seguir alquilándole la infraestructura a sus propios competidores. Durante veinte años construimos tecnología B2B de distribución —APIs, white-label, Music Blocks modulares, royalty reporting, protección contra streaming artificial, un MCP server conversacional— para sellos, agregadores y plataformas que no quieren depender de una major para existir." data-en="limbo/ exists because independent music couldn't keep renting infrastructure from its own competitors. For twenty years we've been building B2B distribution technology (APIs, white-label, modular Music Blocks, royalty reporting, artificial-streaming protection, a conversational MCP server) for labels, aggregators, and platforms that refuse to depend on a major to exist.">limbo/ exists because independent music couldn't keep renting infrastructure from its own competitors. For twenty years we've been building B2B distribution technology (APIs, white-label, modular Music Blocks, royalty reporting, artificial-streaming protection, a conversational MCP server) for labels, aggregators, and platforms that refuse to depend on a major to exist.</p>

        <p data-es="Somos bootstrapped. Sin majors, sin VCs, sin cuerdas. Pertenecemos a Merlin. Somos YouTube Tier A Partner. Clientes como Real World Studios, UN Live, EarthPercent. Lo importante no es la lista: es que cada uno eligió no firmar con nadie que en el futuro pudiera comprarlos." data-en="We're bootstrapped. No majors, no VCs, no strings. Members of Merlin. A YouTube Tier A Partner. Clients like Real World Studios, UN Live, EarthPercent. The list is not the point; the point is that each of them chose not to sign with anyone who might one day buy them.">We're bootstrapped. No majors, no VCs, no strings. Members of Merlin. A YouTube Tier A Partner. Clients like Real World Studios, UN Live, EarthPercent. The list is not the point; the point is that each of them chose not to sign with anyone who might one day buy them.</p>

        <blockquote class="pullquote" data-es="«Own the infrastructure, or you're renting.»" data-en="«Own the infrastructure, or you're renting.»">«Own the infrastructure, or you're renting.»</blockquote>

        <p data-es="La misión, declarada sin rodeos: hacer crecer el PIB global de la música independiente hecha por humanos. No ser el distribuidor más grande del mundo. Agrandar la torta entera." data-en="The mission, stated plainly: grow the global GDP of independent human-made music. Not to be the biggest distributor in the world. To grow the whole pie.">The mission, stated plainly: grow the global GDP of independent human-made music. Not to be the biggest distributor in the world. To grow the whole pie.</p>

        <p data-es="En paralelo trabajo en Beatcoin Music, un musicverse DAO sobre Solana: mi hipótesis sobre cómo se verá la atribución de derechos en la post-IA. El blockchain no se adoptó cuando debía. Ya no está en discusión si hace falta: solo cuándo." data-en="In parallel I'm building Beatcoin Music, a musicverse DAO on Solana: my hypothesis for what rights attribution will look like after AI. The industry didn't adopt blockchain when it should have. It's no longer a question of whether it's needed, only when.">In parallel I'm building Beatcoin Music, a musicverse DAO on Solana: my hypothesis for what rights attribution will look like after AI. The industry didn't adopt blockchain when it should have. It's no longer a question of whether it's needed, only when.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;" data-es="Para saber más sobre la empresa: <a href=&quot;https://limbomusic.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; class=&quot;inline-link&quot;>limbomusic.com</a>" data-en="More about the company: <a href=&quot;https://limbomusic.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; class=&quot;inline-link&quot;>limbomusic.com</a>">More about the company: <a href="https://limbomusic.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-link">limbomusic.com</a></p>
